item.description: LEWIS THIS IS SO EXCITING!!!! i've been incredibly busy these past two weeks but i decided that i absolutely had to read more of your blog deal, and i'm so happy that you're recording everything. It's gonna help me a lot in my political group. anyway i'm going to finish reading about it before i write more... get hilary clinton's autograph and tell her that i am a HUGE fan and supporter!!!!

item.title: By: Emmy

item.description: Lewis, This is so cool. I just listened to NPR in the car about Hilary's strong line with a two party state. How amazing that you are there in the thick of it all. We miss you here, but are so excited for you. xxo Love Emmy

Lewis,
